SpectrumCircle is an AI-powered support system for the autism and neurodiversity
community. If you use, fork, or build upon this project, please:

  1. Keep the copyright notice above intact in all copies.
  2. Credit the original project and author in any public derivative work.
  3. Honor the mission: this software was built to support neurodivergent
     individuals and their families — please use it responsibly and ethically.
